term
Discworld player help
term

Name
.SI 5
term - Set your terminal type.
.EI

Syntax
.SI 5
term <terminal-type>
.EI

Description
.SP 5 5
Term sets your terminal type. If you experiment with terminal types it is your
own fault if your terminal hangs...which it may do if it is not compatible.
Currently supported are dumb, ansi, freedom and ansi-status.  At the moment
only ansi supports different colours.  If you have the terminal codes
for another terminal you would like to see added, please mail one of
the creators.

Share and enjoy.
.EP

See also
.SI 5
cols, rows, review.
.EI
